{"tid":51600,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【急】【元朗巴打召喚】有冇元朗區既醫生好介紹？","createTime":"2016-12-23T10:52:40.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T14:13:01.000Z","uid":8496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"712ea7b11a17cb3d061d07b93738b12d580b28f0","tid":51600,"uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T10:52:40.000Z","msg":"我見朋友係group chat度講到自己病情好嚴重咁，發左幾日燒，睇埋醫生都未退過。<br />\n<br />\n我好擔心佢，我叫佢睇醫生又話唔知睇邊個真係有用，但我又唔熟元朗區既醫生，有冇巴打有好介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41c6fe6e96e232034528ad39538671cfe5f2d662","tid":51600,"uid":52559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T10:57:40.000Z","msg":"入醫院 因住燒壞腦"},{"pid":"4f8e8193aff584c635870361602631f2403c2036","tid":51600,"uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T10:58:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入醫院 因住燒壞腦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n等急症咪盞佢等等下都變壞"},{"pid":"5cb3db6b442a283fb28121740107f2765172de49","tid":51600,"uid":59219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T11:08:09.000Z","msg":"陳嘉龍個間醫務所都幾有用 check得好仔細<br />\n但都係要等"},{"pid":"c9ecf68bf084521feef0143788ad981ef1e6d9fc","tid":51600,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T11:20:04.000Z","msg":"李信華"},{"pid":"523c6b18dfb440db254d61b549df84ec0c54ae82","tid":51600,"uid":32531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T11:21:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>入醫院 因住燒壞腦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n等急症咪盞佢等等下都變壞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁都唔去醫院真係小心"},{"pid":"234a3e8d4f23c77e0e8c9033803afd0dac31571a","tid":51600,"uid":52559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T11:36:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>入醫院 因住燒壞腦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n等急症咪盞佢等等下都變壞</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都發左幾日燒唔差在等果幾粒鐘"},{"pid":"2cf5c0dd0033d31f15df4819ede8001397821e12","tid":51600,"uid":8496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T14:13:01.000Z","msg":"連登有愛，佢一陣就飛的去博愛<br />\n<br />\n因為佢頭先睇醫生時，醫生話佢再唔退就要照肺，所以我地都逼佢去排急症<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}